data.message: Great ,trying to solve your country problems using technology , i hope you the best , and this is great idea ! Go ahead (Y)

First things first, lose the .tk TLD. I know free is tempting but you can't expect people to take you seriously with a free domain name, commonly associated with redirect urls and spammers. 

The company controlling the TLD, freenom is also notoriously known for taking over domain names without prior notice.

If you're a for-profit organization, consider a .com or even better, a .com.eg

If you're a not for-profit organization then consider a .org. Again, .org.eg is even better though harder to get.

Change the Domain extention
And it's a great Idea (y)
